00046 struct null_ctx {
00047 };
00048 
00049 static
00050 __u32 gss_import_sec_context_null(rawobj_t *inbuf, struct gss_ctx *gss_context)
00051 {
00052         struct null_ctx *null_context;
00053 
00054         if (inbuf == NULL || inbuf->data == NULL)
00055                 return GSS_S_FAILURE;
00056 
00057         OBD_ALLOC_PTR(null_context);
00058         if (null_context == NULL)
00059                 return GSS_S_FAILURE;
00060 
00061         gss_context->internal_ctx_id = null_context;
00062         CDEBUG(D_SEC, "successfully imported null context\n");
00063 
00064         return GSS_S_COMPLETE;
00065 }
00066 
00067 static
00068 __u32 gss_copy_reverse_context_null(struct gss_ctx *gss_context_old,
00069                                     struct gss_ctx *gss_context_new)
00070 {
00071         struct null_ctx *null_context_old;
00072         struct null_ctx *null_context_new;
00073 
00074         OBD_ALLOC_PTR(null_context_new);
00075         if (null_context_new == NULL)
00076                 return GSS_S_FAILURE;
00077 
00078         null_context_old = gss_context_old->internal_ctx_id;
00079         memcpy(null_context_new, null_context_old, sizeof(*null_context_new));
00080         gss_context_new->internal_ctx_id = null_context_new;
00081         CDEBUG(D_SEC, "successfully copied reverse null context\n");
00082 
00083         return GSS_S_COMPLETE;
00084 }

00184 int __init init_null_module(void)
00185 {
00186         int status;
00187 
00188         status = lgss_mech_register(&gss_null_mech);
00189         if (status)
00190                 CERROR("Failed to register null gss mechanism!\n");
00191 
00192         return status;
00193 }
